trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element in an MSBuild project.
trans-unit.target: Representa um elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) em um projeto do MSBuild.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object that represents the <see langword="Task" /> element to add to the <see langword="Target" /> element.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> que representa o elemento <see langword="Task" /> a ser adicionado ao elemento <see langword="Target" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) element to the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o elemento [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) especificado ao elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca).

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object represents a child <c>Task</c> element of the <c>Target</c> element.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> representa um elemento <c>Task</c> filho do elemento <c>Target</c>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor de atributo <c>Condition</c> do elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca).

trans-unit.source: The <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O <c>condição</c> valor de atributo de <c>destino</c> elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>DependsOnTargets</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element, which is a semicolon-separated list.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor de atributo <c>DependsOnTargets</c> do elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca), que é uma lista separada por ponto e vírgulas.

trans-unit.source: The <c>DependsOnTargets</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O <c>DependsOnTargets</c> valor de atributo de <c>destino</c> elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um enumerador que itera por meio dos objetos <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> para os objetos <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" />.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método permite que o chamador usar o `foreach` instrução de linguagem c# (`for each` na [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) para percorrer o indivíduo <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objetos no <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objeto representa um elemento filho do `Target` elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the items that are to be input into this target.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define os itens que devem ser de entrada para este destino.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the items.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que representa os itens.

trans-unit.source: Items inside this target attribute are used as the inputs in the top level dependency analysis.
trans-unit.target: Itens dentro desse atributo de destino são usados como entradas na análise de dependência de nível superior.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) foi importado para o projeto.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <c>Target</c> element was imported into the project; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o <c>destino</c> elemento foi importado para o projeto; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>Name</c> attribute value of the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor de atributo <c>Name</c> do elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca).

trans-unit.source: The <c>Name</c> attribute value of the <c>Target</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O <c>nome</c> valor de atributo de <c>destino</c> elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the expected outputs of this target.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define as saídas esperadas deste destino.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the outputs.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que representa as saídas.

trans-unit.source: You can apply transforms to this target attribute to transform a set of input items into a set of output items.
trans-unit.target: Você pode aplicar transformações para esse atributo de destino para transformar um conjunto de itens de entrada em um conjunto de itens de saída.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is used not only for top level dependency analysis but also for the purposes of defining this targets outputs.
trans-unit.target: Este atributo é usado, não apenas para análise de dependência de nível superior, mas também para a finalidade de definir este saídas de destinos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> object that represents the <see langword="Task" /> element to remove from the <see langword="Target" /> element.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask" /> que representa o elemento <see langword="Task" /> a ser removido do elemento <see langword="Target" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) element from the [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element.
trans-unit.target: Remove o elemento [Task](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d82e2485-e5f0-4936-a357-745bacccc299) especificado do elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca).

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objeto representa um filho `Task` elemento o `Target` elemento.
